column2: SELECT p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.dered_u, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, p.dered_i, p.dered_z, p.clean, p.flags , z.z as photoz, z.zErr as photozErr, s.specObjID as specObjID, s.z as specz, s.zErr as speczErr , dbo.fPhotoFlagsN (p.flags) as note FROM GALAXY as p LEFT OUTER JOIN photoz as z ON z.objID = p.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN specObjAll as s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID , dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as near WHERE p.objID = near.objID
